column3: Very fast and reliable calculator, touch screen is a big plus. The help menu is a great guide and the conversion features is very helpful. Ads can be annoying but they don't pop up offline. One thing it is missing is a button to find the 'n' th root of a number, other than that it has pretty much ev...Full ReviewVery fast and reliable calculator, touch screen is a big plus. The help menu is a great guide and the conversion features is very helpful. Ads can be annoying but they don't pop up offline. One thing it is missing is a button to find the 'n' th root of a number, other than that it has pretty much everything.

Calculator is good. But Annoying Ads popup suddenly inbetween the calculations.  Ads will distract, and may cause mistake while typing numbers.  I understand app developers need money through ads, but it's very bad to popup ads inbetween calculations

This calculator does a lot more than it appears to at first glance. Check out the mode button and the brief instructions to reveal complex number calculations, number base conversions/calculations, and more. Yes it has adverts, but only as you log out. How else would the developer continue to be abl...Full ReviewThis calculator does a lot more than it appears to at first glance. Check out the mode button and the brief instructions to reveal complex number calculations, number base conversions/calculations, and more. Yes it has adverts, but only as you log out. How else would the developer continue to be able to produce the software? I've used it for several months, and I've never had any issues with the calculator other than the same finger trouble I experience when typing text messages and emails, and that is most likely my own poor coordination. It's a full 5 from me!
